		<defName>UB_ZCB_ScarredVeteranTribal</defName>
		<title>scarred veteran</title>
		<titleShort>scarred</titleShort>
		<baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef] fought to protect [PAWN_possessive] tribe, sustaining permenant injuries that plagued [PAWN_objective] into adulthood.</baseDesc>
